veratramine in incubations of male and female RLMs in the presence of NADPH and b for the formation of veratramine-3-O-sulfate in incubations of male and female RLCs in the presence of PAPS. Each data point is expressed as mean ± SD of triplicates. Insert figures, Eadie-Hofstee plots", "Proposed in vivo biotransformation schematic of veratramine in male and female rats"]}
